  <p>
    I'm Executive Director of the <a href="https://ocmeco.org">Open Commercial Media Ecosystem (OCME)</a>,
    a member-governed alternative to gatekeeper-controlled creator platforms.
  </p>

  <p>
    Background: BS Mechanical Engineering, PMP. I came up through engineering, product management,
    and smart-contract development before going full-time on OCME in August 2025.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>What I'm good at:</strong> turning ambiguous problems into shipped products, leading
    cross-functional teams, and translating between engineering, business, and users.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>What I care about:</strong> I believe the identity layer is the substrate everything
    digital is built on, and that people should own it. That conviction drives OCME — but the
    operator habits behind it (clear specs, tight feedback loops, shipping) travel to any product.
  </p>

